  "title": "E-Commerce Officer (Senoko)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Maintain product listings, pricing, and inventory across e-commerce platforms <strong>(Shopee, Lazada, Qoo10, e-shop).</strong></li><li>Execute basic online marketing and content updates for social media and company website.</li><li>Prepare simple design materials for product visuals, ads, and promotions.</li><li>Perform ad hoc tasks as required.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma or equivalent</li><li>At least <strong>2 years of e-commerce experience with basic graphic design skills.</strong></li><li>Able to work independently and meet deadlines.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
